OptionTagsWithDisabled
======================

Updates Form option tag helpers to allow you to specify disabled options.

As it stands, the form helpers in rails do not allow you to specify disabled
option tags. This plugin overrides the helpers to add support for disabled options
while maintaining backwards compatibility with the existing API.

